I dont know why im updating, i have nothing to write about, so literally, here goes nothing.........Well since Sunday i have been babysitting, and so far the between working with my dad, and babysittin i have made $190, and i still have to work tomarrow morning...so ill end up with prolly around $240, and ive spent 150 already,and i dont even know what on. Sooo... i get done working today at around 5:30, and i plan on going to the mall, to get a few shirts, then back up to Montag, for the boring sit at home stuff.  
I cant wait until football season, our first game is against a top 5 in state team, Mendon, they are suppose to be bad@ss, but they wont be sh!t to us. :) Well , i dont know what else to write about, so peace

WHAT A DAY! First thing: squated a new max of 425, got my 250 shirt finally (i did it about a month ago and just got the shirt). Then at tech center, the teacher has me marked for 5 unexcused absenses, which i havent been absent from yet without being excused, and i started bitchin about it because it lowers your grade, and got in trouble. On the way home from tech center i was trying to sleep, and a kid on the bus thought he would be cool and slam my head into the window twice, then i told him to not do it again, he did it, and i got kicked off the bus for breakin his nose, and busting skin on his forhead (big bloody mess) and i think my hand hurts more than his face does, i think i broke something, but oh well, i snapped, and it was kinda nice getting some stress out! WHAT A DAY EH?! OH and Sarah, if you read this, please just give me a call or email me or something, i need to talk to you!!! So PlEaSe Get ahold of me!!!
